data.description: The Ruby is a two-story floorplan with ample living space, featuring four bedrooms and two and a half baths. The first floor is an open concept space including the kitchen, dining, and great room. The second floor boasts four secondary bedrooms, two bathrooms, laundry room, and a large loft space. The spacious primary bedroom includes a comfortable sitting area, spacious bathroom, and walk-in closet. Photos are a depiction of a similar home. Owners will enjoy world class amenities including resort style pool, club house, indoor pickle ball court, bocce ball court, playground, gas fire pit, and boat launch.
